{
  "stem": "26983.12",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was enough that they got a-- a kind of conserve of food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they swallowed it, and they died.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- We were lucky because of the soldier.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we got-- But in that hospital, did you get a good--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we got a normal, good treatment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had, I remember, 10 or 12 days, a very high fever-- 40, 41.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we survived it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were Catholic nurses who nursed us back to life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember very well, the very first day I could go out of bed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I guess, Austrian nurses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I looked in a mirror after many years, and it was very unpleasant.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, it's impossible, such ugly and terrible face.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was shocked to see my face.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But slowly, we recovered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had enough strength to continue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that is a story for itself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He helped us, first of all, to be able to continue our way back to Prague.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He wrote some letters of recommendation and so on, which helped us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the normal procedure was, at the time of the war, from the American zone, to go to the Russian zone.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from the Russian zone-- I think that time Vienna was under the Russian occupation-- we could take our way to Prague.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what happened?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, they took all us in a camp after the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There is also one beautiful story from Gunskirchen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Near Gunskirchen was a train of the German soldiers who just left the train and escaped.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we children-- the American soldiers-- I remember the very first negro I saw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, today you say the black-- In the American army?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Army.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let us go in the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
